title: The American Legion National Commander to Attend Congressional Hearing Probing Misuse of VA Relocation Program ...
text: --(BUSINESS WIRE)--The American Legion: WHO: Dale Barnett, National Commander of the 2.2 million member American Legion WHAT: National Commander Barnett, of Douglasville, Ga., has rescheduled his itinerary to attend a House Committee on Veterans’ Affairs hearing which will examine a recent IG report which found exorbitant relocation expenses paid on behalf of Philadelphia Regional Office Director Diana Rubens.
